ing%20over%20Russia%20on%20US%20routes.%20Instead%2C%20these%20carriers%20would%20be%20forced%20to%20fly%20longer%2C%20less%20efficient%20paths%20%E2%80%94%20possibly%20adding%20multiple%20hours%20of%20extra%20flight%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20order%20targets%20seven%20airlines%2C%20including%20Air%20China%2C%20Beijing%20Capital%20Airlines%2C%20China%20Eastern%20Airlines%2C%20China%20Southern%20Airlines%2C%20Hainan%20Airlines%2C%20Sichuan%20Airlines%2C%20and%20Xiamen%20Airlines.%20Hong%20Kong-based%20Cathay%20Pacific%20Airways%20was%20not%20named.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20DoT%20said%20barring%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-uses-airspace-restrict-airliners-make-politic-moves-siberian-corridor-2021-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EChinese%20airlines%20from%20flying%20over%20Russia%3C%2Fa%3E%20would%20address%20a%20%26quot%3Bcompetitive%20disparity%26quot%3B%20for%20US%20carriers%3B%20it%20excluded%20cargo%20carriers%20from%20the%20order.%20The%20agency%20added%20that%20Chinese%20airlines%20enjoy%20an%20%26quot%3Bunequal%26quot%3B%20advantage%20by%20avoiding%20the%20added%20time%20and%20fuel%20costs%20of%20detouring%20around%20Russian%20airspace.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20airlines%2C%20such%20as%20American%2C%20Delta%2C%20and%20United%2C%20must%20fly%20less%20economical%20flight%20paths%20as%20they%20are%20barred%20from%20using%20Russian%20airspace%20amid%20sanctions%20over%20the%20nation's%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine.%20It%20also%20strains%20maintenance%2C%20aircraft%20utilization%2C%20and%20crew%20rest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnited%20declined%20to%20comment.%20American%20and%20Delta%20referred%20Business%20Insider%20to%20their%20trade%20group%2C%20Airlines%20for%20America%2C%20which%20also%20represents%20United.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20an%20important%20step%20that%20will%20help%20ensure%20U.S.%20airlines%20can%20compete%20with%20Chinese%20carriers%20on%20a%20level%20playing%20field%2C%26quot%3B%20A4A%20said%20in%20an%20earlier%20press%20sta