%5C%22595%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFlightaware%20screenshot%20of%20the%20China%20Eastern%20flight%20path%20between%20JFK%20and%20Shanghai%20over%20Russia%20in%20October.%3Cp%3EFlightaware%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20routes%20are%20about%2015%20and%2016%20hours%20nonstop%2C%20respectively.%20However%2C%20being%20forced%20to%20skirt%20Russian%20borders%2C%20should%20the%20order%20take%20effect%2C%20could%20add%20hours%20of%20flight%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffinnair-airlounge-business-class-seat-pod-review-photos-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EFinnair%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20for%20example%2C%20has%20flown%20four%20hours%20longer%20between%20Helsinki%20and%20Tokyo%20since%20Russia%20closed%20its%20airspace%20to%20most%20European%20carriers.%20British%20Airways%20is%20adding%20up%20to%20an%20extra%20hour%20to%20its%20flights%20between%20London%20and%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20US-China%20routes%2C%20such%20as%20Hainan's%20flight%20between%20Seattle%20and%20Chongqing%2C%20Xiamen's%20flight%20between%20New%20York%20and%20Fuzhou%2C%20and%20Air%20China's%20flight%20between%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20and%20Beijing%2C%20all%20avoid%20Russia%2C%20according%20to%20Flightaware%20data%20for%20October.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f3af8949-779a-4ce7-82d1-8ff6c4f4bf3d%5C%22%3EUS%20airlines%20have%20long%20complained%20about%20China's%20flying%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Big%203%20airlines%20have%20long%20expressed%20frustration%20with%20the%20Biden-era%20decision%20in%202024%20to%20allow%20Chinese%20carriers%20to%20operate%20up%20to%2050%20weekly%20roundtrip%20flights%20to%20the%20US%20%E2%80%94%20up%20from%2035%20and%20matching%20the%20number%20allowed%20for%20US%20airlines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Big%203%20had%20urged%20the%20DoT%20not%20to%20approve%20the%20additional%20flights%20unless%20the%20Chinese%20airlines%20avoided%20Russian%20airspace.%20That%20followed%20a%202023%20agreement%20in%20which%20the%20US%20allowed%20some%20new%20Chinese%20routes%20on%20the%20condition%20that%20they%20did%20not%20overfly%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20flights%20aren't%20always%20cheap%2C%20given%20the%20few%20options.%20Round-trip%20fares%20range%20from%20about%20%24900%20from%20Seattle%20to%20Shanghai%20in%20mid-November%20on%20Delta%2C%20to%20between%20%241%2C200%20and%20%241%2C500%20from%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20carrier.%20The%20nonstop%20flight%20from%20New%20York%20to%20Guangzhou%20on%20China%20Southern%20is%20nearly%20%242%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Chinese%20carriers%20got%20more%20flying%2C%20US%20carriers%20have%20had%20to%20ax%20some%20China%20routes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EData%20from%20aviation%20analytics%20company%20Cirium%20shows%20that%20United%2C%20for%20example%2C%20has%20not%20resumed%20flights%20to%20China%20from%20Chicago%2C%20Washington%2C%20D.C.%2C%20and%20Newark%2C%20New%20Jersey%2C%20since%20the%20pandemic%2C%20but%20it%20operates%20from%20the%20West%20Coast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDelta%20still%20isn't%20operating%20its%20flight%20from%20Atlanta%20to%20Shanghai%2C%20although%20it%20does%20fly%20there%20from%20Detroit%20and%20Seattle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20last%20year's%20increase%2C%20flights%20between%20the%20US%20and%20China%20are%20still%20recovering%20from%20the%20pandemic.%20Cirium%20shows%20there%20are%20about%2010%2C000%20flights%20scheduled%20between%20the%20two%20nations%20in%202025%20across%20both%20US%20and%20Chinese%20airlines.%20That's%20down%2028%25%20from%20about%2035%2C500%20flights%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222968dde3-6e70-46e1-962b-6b2dd81ecbdf%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESecurity%20concerns%20of%20flying%20over%20Russia%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20economic%20concerns%2C%20there%20are%20security%20implications%20regarding%20US-bound%20flights%20over%20Russia.%20In%20June%202023%20and%20July%202024%2C%20two%20separate%20San%20Francisco-bound%20Air%20India%20flights%20likely%20carrying%20Americans%20had%20to%20divert%20to%20Russia%20due%20to%20a%20technical%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20concern%20that%20geopolitical%20tensions%20could%20threaten%20any%20onboard%20US%20citizens%2C%20though%20none%20were%20detained%2C%20and%20a%20relief%20plane%20was%20sent%20to%20rescue%20the%20stranded%20passengers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20United%20CEO%20Scott%20Kirby%20raised%20questions%20about%20allowing%20foreign%20airlines%20to%20continue%20flying%20over%20Russia%20on%20US%20routes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat's%20going%20to%20happen%20if%20an%20airline%20lands%20in%20Russia%20with%20some%20prominent%20US%20citizens%20on%20board%3F%20That%20is%20a%20potential%20crisis%20in%20the%20making%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20after%20the%202023%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20uncommon%20for%20leaders%20to%20block%20flight%20paths%20through%20their%20nation%20due%20to%20economic%20tensions%20or%20war.%20The%20US%20and%20Russia%20have%20reciprocally%20blocked%20their%20airspace%20from%20each%20other's%20home%20carriers%20since%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fairlines-cancel-and-reroute-flights-as-iran-conflict-intensifies-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAirspaces%20across%20the%20Middle%20East%20were%20closed%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20June%20and%20July%20due%20to%20heightened%20tensions%20between%20Iran%20and%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fair-india-flights-extra-hours-to-avoid-closed-pakistan-airspace-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPakistan%20closed%20its%20airspace%20to%20Indian%20airlines%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20April%20amid%20rising%20tensions%20in%20the%20area%2C%20and%20India%20responded%20with%20its%20own%20closure%20to%20Pakistani%20aircraft%20soon%20after.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fair-india-suspending-delhi-washington-us-route-pakista