0made-to-order%2C%20I%20opted%20for%20the%20one%20color%20that%20was%20in%20stock%2C%20Sable.%20Sitting%20somewhere%20between%20brown%20and%20gray%2C%20Sable%20is%20a%20great%20neutral%20that%20can%20fit%20in%20just%20about%20any%20space.%20In%20my%20case%2C%20it%20landed%20in%20my%20kids'%20playroom%2C%20where%20we%20were%20desperately%20in%20need%20of%20a%20seating%20option%20that%20was%20comfortable%20and%20could%20withstand%20the%20trials%20and%20mess%20of%20childhood.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EQuince's%20sofas%20are%20made%20in%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20which%20is%20a%20major%20plus%20in%20today's%20climate.%20Due%20to%20a%20high%2025%25%20tariff%20recently%20imposed%20on%20furniture%20made%20overseas%2C%20the%20Quince%20Sierra%20Sofa%20could%20potentially%20avoid%20price%20hikes%20that%20will%20soon%20be%20imposed%20on%20a%20lot%20of%20competitors%2C%20but%20the%20complete%20effects%20remain%20to%20be%20seen.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20bench%20seat%20cushions%20are%20filled%20with%20a%20foam%20and%20recycled%20fiber%20blend.%20The%20combo%20is%20intended%20to%20mimic%20the%20comfort%20of%20down%20without%20the%20need%20for%20fluffing%2C%20a%20claim%20I%20found%20it%20achieved%20well.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20sofa's%20frame%20is%20constructed%20of%20solid%20wood%20and%20ultra-durable%20kiln-dried%20engineered%20wood%2C%20all%20certified%20by%20the%20Sustainable%20Forestry%20Initiative.%20The%20frame%20joinery%20is%20glued%2C%20corner%20blocked%2C%20and%20fastened%2C%20all%20qualities%20of%20a%20high-quality%20and%20stable%20design.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f1fd5486-1140-4365-921d-16b2801a9397%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Ordering%20and%20delivery%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EOrdering%20and%20delivery%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Quince%20sofa%20upside%20down%20in%20plastic%20during%20delivery%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68e951455dbc4fd10daaa641%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETwo%20movers%20unpacked%20and%20setup%20my%20sofa%20within%2010%20minutes.%20%3Cp%3EMorgan%20Flaherty%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShipping%20time%20for%20the%20Sierra%20Sofa%20can%20vary%2C%20with%20in-stock%20models%20available%20to%20ship%20in%20about%20two%20to%20three%20weeks%2C%20while%20made-to-order%20options%20take%20six%20to%20eight%20weeks.%20When%20browsing%20on%20the%20site%2C%20the%20page%20clearly%20marks%20which%20shade%20options%20are%20currently%20stocked%2C%20versus%20which%20will%20require%20longer%20made-to-order%20shipping%20and%20delivery.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20Quince%20is%20a%20direct-to-consumer%2C%20online%20only%20business%2C%20you%20won't%20have%20the%20option%20to%20test%20the%20sofa%20or%20any%20of%20the%20brand's%20furniture%20in%20a%20showroom.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20delivery%20can%20take%20a%20while%2C%20the%20actual%20process%20of%20delivery%20is%20a%20major%20highlight.%20Quince%20offers%20free%20white%20glove%20delivery%20for%20their%20furniture%2C%20allowing%20you%20to%20have%20readily%20assembled%20pieces%20delivered%20to%20the%20room%20of%20your%20choice%20without%20a%20delivery%20fee.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20my%20Sierra%20Sofa%20was%20ready%20for%20delivery%2C%20I%20was%20contacted%20by%20e-mail%20and%20given%20several%20date%20options%20to%20choose%20from.%20On%20the%20day%20I%20selected%2C%20I%20was%20given%20a%20timeframe%20during%20which%20two%20movers%20showed%20up%20with%20my%20fully%20assembled%20sofa%2C%20with%20a%20phone%20call%20to%20confirm%20the%20movers%20were%20on%20their%20way.%20The%20sofa%20arrived%20wrapped%20in%20plastic%20to%20keep%20the%20fabric%20clean%2C%20and%2C%20from%20arrival%20to%20set%20up%2C%20the%20movers%20had%20my%20piece%20ready%20and%20in%20the%20room%20of%20my%20choice%20within%20about%2010%20minutes.%20The%20fact%20that%20delivery%20is%20free%20and%20can%20be%20done%20to%20any%20floor%20of%20the%20house%20is%20a%20huge%20benefit%20offered%20by%20Quince%20when%20compared%20to%20competitors%2C%20in%20my%20opinion.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20with%20any%20online-only%20order%2C%20it%20can%20feel%20like%20a%20major%20risk%20taking%20on%20such%20a%20big%20purchase%20sight%20unseen.%20Quince%20does%20offer%20returns%20for%20furniture%2C%20though%20they%20must%20be%20initiated%20within%20seven%20days%20of%20delivery%2C%20a%20departure%20from%20its%20typical%20yearlong%20return%20window%20on%20apparel%20and%20home%20products.%20Returns%20are%20subject%20to%20a%2015%25%20restocking%20fee%2C%20so%20you'll%20want%20to%20be%20sure%20before%20you%20commit.%20The%20brand%20also%20offers%20very%20little%20in%20terms%20of%20a%20warranty.%20The%20frames%20of%20the%20sofas%20come%20with%20a%20lifetime%20guarantee%20(specified%20as%20%26quot%3Breasonable%2C%20non-commercial%2C%20household%20use%26quot%3B)%2C%20but%20almost%20all%20other%20defects%20are%20not%20covered%20by%20any%20type%20of%20extended%20warranty.%20That's%20worth%20noting%20compared%20to%20brands%20like%20Interior%20Define%20or%20Joybird%2C%20which%20offer%20a%20more%20generous%20warranty%20with%20their%20furniture.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ce121d9c-bdf4-44aa-9429-6514ac56681d%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Comfort%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EComfort%20and%20real-life%20usage%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223240%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Quince%20sofa%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68e951e2cc993f9955cfff6d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222430%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20cushions%20strike%20a%20nice%20balance%20between%20soft%20and%20supportive.%3Cp%3EMorgan%20Flaherty%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20quality%20that%20immediately%20drew%20me%20to%20the%20Sierra%20Sofa%20was%20how%20comfortable%20it%20looked.%20The%20sofa%20has%20deep%20seats%2C%20making%20it%20an%20ideal%20spot%20for%20lounging%20in%20the%20playroom%20while%20watching%20both%20kids.%20The%20cushions%20strike%20a%20nice%20balance%20between%20soft%20and%20supportive%3A%20they're%20not%20overly%20firm%2C%20but%20not%20so%20plush%20that%20you%20sink%20down%20uncomfortably.%20Having%20one%20long%20seat%20cushion%20as%20opposed%20to%20two%20is%20also%20ideal%20for%20a%20playroom%20setting%2C%20where%20crumbs%20and%20toys%20can%20easily%20get%20lost%20in%20between%20two%20seat%20cushions%20(something%20I%20say%20confidently%20from%20past%20experience).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20supportive%20and%20cozy%20back%20cushions%20are%20made%20with%20recycled%20polyfiber.%20Notably%2C%20they%20rise%20higher%20than%20the%20back%20of%20the%20couch%20itself.%20The%20height%20difference%20lends%20itself%20well%20to%20the%20general%20aesthetics%20of%20the%20sofa%20but%20also%20reduces%20some%20of%20the%20back%20support%2C%20as%20it%20doesn't%20allow%20you%20to%20lie%20comfortably%20all%20the%20way%20back.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20armrests%20are%20wide%20and%20gently%20curved%2C%20which%20makes%20them%20surprisingly%20comfortable%20for%20propping%20a%20pillow%20or%20leaning%20against%20during%20a%20nap.%20They%20also%20provide%20enough%20room%20for%20putting%20down%20a%20baby%20bottle%20or%20a%20cup%20(if%20you're%20feeling%20daring).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20the%207-foot%20couch%2C%20I%20can%20honestly%20say%20it's%20become%20a%20favorite%20napping%20spot%20for%20both%20my%20toddler%20and%20me.%20On%20mornings%20when%20my%20three-year-old%20wakes%20me%20up%20before%20the%20crack%20of%20dawn%2C%20I've%20sometimes%20had%20to%20stop%20myself%20from%20sinking%20in%20and%20getting%20a%20bit%20of%20shut-eye%20on%20the%20Sierra%20Sofa%2C%20because%20it's%20all%20too%20easy%20to%20fall%20asleep%20on%20it.%20While%20I%20don't%20know%20that%20the%20couch%20would%20be%20my%20first%20choice%20for%20spending%20a%20full%20night%20of%20sleep%2C%20for%20shorter%20naps%20and%20relaxation%2C%20the%20cushions%20and%20depth%20of%20the%20couch%20certainly%20fit%20the%20bill%20for%20a%20nice%20nap%20spot.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlong%20with%20a%20bit%20of%20sleep%2C%20I've%20also%20spent%20a%20few%20marathon%20sessions%20on%20the%20Sierra%20Sofa%20working%20from%20home.%20It's%20provided%20an%20ideal%20spot%20for%20comfortably%20working%20on%20my%20computer%20for%20a%20few%20hours%20at%20a%20time.%20The%20wide%20armrests%20provide%20a%20great%20spot%20to%20prop%20up%20my%20laptop%2C%20while%20the%20seat%20cushion%20has%20held%20up%20as%20a%20comfortable%20spot%20to%20sit%20for%20longer%20periods%20of%20time.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221ecd9613-2f64-46cb-b71d-626029a8b6e7%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Durability%20and%20quality%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EDurability%20and%20quality%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20you%20have%20two%20young%20kids%2C%20no%20furniture%20is%20completely%20safe%20from%20stains%2C%20scuffs%2C%20and%20overuse.%20One%20of%20my%20biggest%20concerns%20with%20the%20Sierra%20Sofa%20was%20the%20fabric.%20I%20was%20immediately%20concerned%20about%20how%20the%20plush%20finish%20would%20hold%20up%20to%20an%20unruly%20toddler%20and%20a%20newborn%20whose%20sole%20purpose%20in%20life%20is%20to%20create%20a%20mess.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETurns%20out%2C%20I%20had%20nothing%20to%20worry%20about%20%E2%80%94%20the%20performance%20velvet%20lives%20up%20to%20its%20name.%20After%20several%20weeks%20of%20real-world%20use%20(during%20which%20time%20I've%20had%20spills%2C%20crayon%20markings%2C%20and%20a%20toddler%20who%20enjoys%20launching%20herself%20onto%20furniture)%2C%20I've%20found%20the%20fabric%20incredibly%20durable.%20There's%20been%20no%20noticeable%20pilling%2C%20and%20stains%20have%20been%20easily%20wiped%20away%20with%20a%20damp%20cloth.%20While%20the%20performance%20velvet%20has%20worked%20out%20well%20so%20far%2C%20I'm%20also%20relieved%20that%20the%20cushions%20all%20come%20with%20covers%20that%20can%20be%20removed%20for%20easy%20cleaning.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThanks%20to%20the%20high-resiliency%20foam%20core%2C%20the%20cushions%20have%20also%20maintained%20their%20shape%20after%20heavy%20use.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20frame%20is%20built%20well%2C%20making%20for%20a%20structure%20that's%20comfortable%20to%20sit%20or%20lie%20on%20and%20keeps%20its%20shape%20after%20plenty%20of%20use.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20couch%20does%20have%20solid%20wood%20feet%2C%20which%20help%20keep%20it%20stable%2C%20but%20they%20also%20sometimes%20tend%20to%20slide%20on%20a%20wooden%20floor.%20It's%20a%20minor%20thing%2C%20and%20in%20some%20ways%2C%20it's%20ideal%2C%20so%20that%20it's%20easier%20to%20move%20around.%20Nevertheless%2C%20if%20you%20plan%20on%20using%20the%20Sierra%20Sofa%20away%20from%20a%20wall%2C%20you'll%20want%20to%20find%20some%20grip%20pads%20to%20put%20on%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20feet%20to%20keep%20it%20from%20moving%20around.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c7ccf66a-9526-4799-a8f3-5dd99b4bd9bf%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Cons%20to%20consider%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ECons%20to%20consider%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20look%20at%20the%20sofa%20arms%20and%20cushions%20going%20above%20the%20back%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68e951451c1f80efbec562c0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20back%20of%20the%20frame%20is%20a%20few%20inches%20lower%20than%20the%20back%20cushions%2C%20which%20sacrifices%20some%20support%2C%20when%20leaning%20back.%20%3Cp%3EMorgan%20Flaherty%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20several%20weeks%20of%20use%2C%20there's%20a%20lot%20to%20love%20about%20the%20Sierra%20Sofa%2C%20from%20the%20price%20tag%20to%20the%20durability.%20However%2C%20there%20are%20also%20some%20key%20downsides%20you'll%20want%20to%20consider.%20Perhaps%20the%20biggest%20is%20the%20fact%20that%20you're%20going%20to%20need%20to%20order%20the%20sofa%20sight%20unseen.%20While%20that's%20the%20case%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20furniture%20brands%20today%2C%20it's%20still%20a%20scary%20prospect%20to%20drop%20a%20large%20chunk%20of%20money%20on%20something%20you%20haven't%20used%20in%20person.%20While%20Quince%20does%20offer%20returns%2C%20they%20need%20to%20be%20requested%20within%20seven%20days%20of%20delivery%2C%20and%20are%20subject%20to%20a%2015%25%20restocking%20fee.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20for%20the%20design%20of%20the%20couch%2C%20my%20family%20and%20I%20have%20also%20all%20been%20slightly%20bothered%20by%20the%20low%20back%20of%20the%20couch%2C%20with%20the%20back%20of%20the%20frame%20a%20few%20inches%20lower%20than%20the%20back%20cushions.%20While%20this%20may%20not%20even%20be%20something%20that%20registers%20for%20all-adult%20households%20who%20can%20sit%20peacefully%2C%20it's%20something%20I've%20noticed%20when%20my%20toddler%20leans%20back%2C%20and%20inevitably%20almost%20throws%20herself%20back%20over%20the%20sofa.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2258dee11a-431d-48e8-89bf-a722fc87be24%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20are%20your%20alternatives%3F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20are%20your%20alternatives%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22the%20article%20riley%20sleeper%20sofa%20with%20a%20dog%20sitting%20on%20it%20and%20throw%20pillows%20added%20on%20top%20of%20it%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68dc7e65cc993f9955cf4217%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Article%20Riley%20sofa%20has%20a%20similar%20boxy%20look.%20It%20has%20individual%20cushions%20instead%20of%20a%20benchseat.%20It's%20comparably%20priced%20(around%20%241%2C700)%20but%20that%20doesn't%20include%20free%20white%20glove%20delivery%20and%20it's%20not%20made%20in%20the%20US.%20The%20Riley%20is%20also%20available%20as%20a%20sofa%20bed%2C%20however.%20%3Cp%3ESarah%20Saril%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EQuince's%20sofa%20selection%20is%20still%20relatively%20curated%2C%20offering%20a%20few%20silhouettes%20in%20various%20lengths%20and%20some%20sectionals.%20Most%20notably%2C%20they%20recently%20introduced%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15116225559hw-20%26h%3De319c286d7554e6719f69b1e04a5f95ed4044770f6dca415c7457ee98f5a151b%26postID%3D68e94d358232dd3f92edbf06%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fquince-sofa-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.quince.com%252Fhome%252Fstillman-performance-velvet-sleeper-sofa%253Fcolor%253Dflax%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Equeen-sized%20sleeper%20sofa%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20that%20costs%20under%20%242%2C000.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20no%20lack%20of%20options%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20finding%20a%20couch%20with%20a%20similar%20modern%2C%20lounge-worthy%20design.%20In%20fact%2C%20visually%2C%20the%20Sierra%20is%20a%20great%20dupe%20of%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Frh.com%2Fus%2Fen%2Fcatalog%2Fcategory%2Fcollections.jsp%2Fcat15830006%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERH%20Modena%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20also%20chooses%20to%20compare%20its%20design%20to%20the%20likes%20of%20Williams%20Sonoma%20brands%20or%20Maiden%20Home%2C%20all%20of%20which%20make%20their%20upholstery%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBenchmade%20Modern%20is%20another%20DTC%20company%20that%20builds%20its%20furniture%20in%20the%20United%20States%20(Dallas%20and%20Los%20Angeles%20specifically)%2C%20but%20its%20most%20affordable%20sofa%20%3Cem%3Estarts%3C%2Fem%3E%20at%20%243%2C000.%20We%20got%20a%20look%20at%20the%20customization%20process%20in%20our%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbenchmade-modern-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBenchmade%20Modern%20review%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20and%20though%20pricey%2C%20it's%20worth%20it%20for%20the%20beautiful%20quality.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20you%20like%20the%20look%20and%20price%20point%20of%20Quince%20but%20want%20more%20options%2C%20check%20out%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15116225559hw-20%26h%3D9dad061c391a4aa7d9796e900d854da6cd4cff14371f75ac62543df42113b3c6%26postID%3D68e94d358232dd3f92edbf06%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fquince-sofa-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.article.com%252Fbrowse%252F12%252Fsofas-sofas%253F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EArticle%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20which%20offers%20similar%20clean-lined%20sofas%20and%20some%20beautiful%20mid-century%20inspired%20options%2C%20but%20with%20a%20broader%20fabric%20and%20size%20selection.%20We%20recently%20tested%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Farticle-sofa-bed-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERiley%20Sofa%20Bed%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20which%20follows%20a%20similar%20boxy%20construction.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.interiordefine.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInterior%20Define%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20another%20brand%20that%20offers%20an%20incredibly%20similar%20design%20to%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.interiordefine.com%2Flee-collection%3Fpage%3D1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELee%20Collection%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20thanks%20to%20its%20thick%20track%20arms%2C%20but%20with%20far%20more%20customizations%20than%20Quince.%20With%20Interior%20Design%2C%20you%20can%20not%20only%20choose%20the%20fabric%20but%20also%20customize%20the%20legs%2C%20depth%2C%20size%2C%20and%20even%20cushion%20fill.%20While%20Quince%20offers%20a%20few%20neutral%20fabric%20options%2C%20Interior%20Design%20may%20be%20worth%20considering%20if%20you%20want%20to%20make%20sure%20your%20furniture%20perfectly%20fits%20your%20space.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20budget-friendly%20furniture%2C%20it's%20hard%20to%20beat%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ikea.com%2Fus%2Fen%2Fcat%2Fsofas-sectionals-fu003%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIkea%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20However%2C%20you'll%20need%20to%20sacrifice%20build%20quality%20and%20white-glove%20service%20with%20this%20option%2C%20meaning%20the%20seating%20may%20not%20last%20as%20long%20as%20other%20options%20(something%20I%20can%20say%20from%20experience%2C%20having%20purchased%20several%20Ikea%20couches%20in%20the%20past).%20None%20of%20these%20companies%20manufactures%20its%20sofas%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20however.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221d7d1e98-722c-46ed-a322-faf7d88dca45%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22The%20bottom%20line%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20bottom%20line%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Quince%20sofa%20with%20gingham%20pillows%20on%20top%20next%20to%20a%20carpet%20sofa%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68e951455dbc4fd10daaa640%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EConsidering%20the%20stylish%20yet%20comfortable%20design%2C%20durable%20performance%20fabrics%2C%20and%20unbeatable%20price%2C%20the%20Quince%20Sofa%20checks%20off%20everything%20I%20was%20looking%20for%20in%20a%20well-made%20sofa.%20%3Cp%3EMorgan%20Flaherty%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigc