%3BThe%20Prophecy%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20(%26quot%3BI'm%20so%20afraid%20I%20sealed%20my%20fate%2C%20no%20sign%20of%20soulmates%26quot%3B).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESwift's%20romantic%20anxiety%20is%20reinforced%20by%20her%20past%20experiences%20with%20dating%20in%20the%20public%20eye%2C%20as%20she%20observes%20in%20the%20first%20verse%20of%20%26quot%3BElizabeth%20Taylor%26quot%3B%20(%26quot%3BAll%20the%20right%20guys%20promised%20they'd%20stay%20%2F%20Under%20bright%20lights%2C%20they%20withered%20away%26quot%3B).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20the%20song's%20bridge%2C%20Swift%20takes%20pride%20in%20the%20body%20of%20work%20she%20has%20built%20off%20those%20disappointments%3A%20%26quot%3BAll%20my%20white%20diamonds%20and%20lovers%20are%20forever%20%2F%20In%20the%20papers%2C%20on%20the%20screen%2C%20and%20in%20their%20minds.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20only%20is%20this%20a%20reference%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Felizabethtaylor.com%2Fwhite-diamonds-and-elizabeths-two-great-loves%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETaylor's%20famous%20collection%20of%20jewels%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20her%20signature%20fragrance%2C%20%26quot%3BWhite%20Diamonds%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20Swift%20seems%20to%20compare%20her%20own%20songs%20to%20precious%20gems%20or%20historical%20artifacts.%20Swift's%20lovers%20and%20experiences%20are%20immortalized%20in%20her%20discography%2C%20much%20like%20the%20enduring%20legacy%20of%20Taylor's%20filmography.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224be5da31-13c6-4063-8dde-8a80898d311d%5C%22%3EThis%20isn't%20the%20first%20time%20Swift%20has%20name-dropped%20Taylor%20in%20a%20song%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222472%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Richard%20Burton%20and%20Elizabeth%20Taylor%20in%20the%201967%20film%20%26quot%3BThe%20Taming%20of%20the%20Shrew.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68e9440c1c1f80efbec56071%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221980%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERichard%20Burton%20and%20Elizabeth%20Taylor%20in%20the%201967%20film%20%26quot%3BThe%20Taming%20of%20the%20Shrew.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ESilver%20Screen%20Collection%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESwift%20previously%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftaylor-swift-lyrics-literary-references-easter-eggs-details-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ereferenced%20Taylor%20in%20%26quot%3B%E2%80%A6Ready%20For%20It%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202017.%20The%20opening%20track%20on%20%26quot%3BReputation%26quot%3B%20is%20about%20the%20thrills%20and%20fantasies%20sparked%20by%20a%20budding%20romance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20can%20be%20my%20jailer%2C%20Burton%20to%20this%20Taylor%20%2F%20Every%20love%20I've%20known%20in%20comparison%20is%20a%20failure%2C%26quot%3B%20Swift%20sings.%20%26quot%3BI%20forget%20their%20names%20now%20%2F%20I'm%20so%20very%20tame%20now%20%2F%20Never%20be%20the%20same%20now.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETaylor%20was%20famously%20married%20twice%20to%20Burton.%20As%20husband%20and%20wife%2C%20they%20costarred%20in%20classic%20films%20like%20%26quot%3BWho's%20Afraid%20of%20Virginia%20Woolf%3F%26quot%3B%20(1966)%20and%20%26quot%3BThe%20Taming%20of%20the%20Shrew%26quot%3B%20(1967).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20keeping%20with%20the%20core%20theme%20of%20Swift's%20sixth%20album%20%26quot%3BReputation%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20love%20and%20tenderness%20coexisting%20with%20scandal%20and%20notoriety%20%E2%80%94%20Wilding%20told%20The%20Guardian%20that%20his%20mother%20was%20the%20%26quot%3Bdominant%20figure%26quot%3B%20in%20her%20relationship%20with%20Burton%3A%20%26quot%3BHe's%20sitting%20there%20quietly%2C%20and%20she's%20protecting%20him%2C%20fending%20off%20reporters%20and%20taking%20charge.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWilding%20also%20said%20he%20never%20questioned%20his%20mother's%20cycle%20of%20marriage%20and%20divorce%2C%20despite%20the%20media%20frenzy%20it%20inspired.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20seemed%20normal%2C%26qu