up%2C%20Worktrace%20AI%2C%20backed%20by%20former%20OpenAI%20CTO%20Mira%20Murati.%20Like%20Murati's%20secretive%20startup%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmira-murati-openai-startup-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EThinking%20Machines%20Lab%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Worktrace%20AI%20focuses%20on%20selling%20AI%20to%20large%20businesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWorktrace%20AI%20was%20in%20talks%20this%20summer%20to%20raise%20a%20seed%20round%20of%20%2410%20million%20at%20a%20%2450%20million%20valuation%2C%20according%20to%20correspondence%20seen%20by%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWorktrace%20AI%20has%20a%20website%20and%20LinkedIn%20page%2C%20but%20it%20has%20not%20made%20any%20public%20announcements%20about%20its%20launch.%20Jiang%20declined%20to%20comment.%20Her%20cofounder%2C%20Deepak%20Vasisht%2C%20an%20assistant%20professor%20of%20computer%20science%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Illinois%2C%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWorktrace%20AI%20helps%20businesses%20find%20and%20automate%20repetitive%20tasks%20by%20observing%20employees%2C%20its%20website%20said.%20It's%20part%20of%20a%20recent%20interest%20in%20Silicon%20Valley%20in%20AI%20learning%20and%20replicating%20human%20tasks.%20Last%20month%2C%20for%20example%2C%20OpenAI%20announced%20new%20methods%20to%20measure%20the%20performance%20of%20its%20models%20on%20real-world%20tasks%2C%20such%20as%20writing%20legal%20briefs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWorktrace%20AI%20has%20attracted%20funding%20from%20a%20who's%20who%20of%20OpenAI%20figures.%20Its%20backers%20include%20Nick%20Turley%2C%20the%20head%20of%20ChatGPT%3B%20Jason%20Kwon%2C%20OpenAI's%20chief%20strategy%20officer%3B%20and%20Joanne%20Jang%2C%20who%20led%20the%20team%20responsible%20for%20shaping%20ChatGPT's%20behavior%2C%20according%20to%20a%20job%20posting%20for%20a%20founding%20engineer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWorktrace%20AI%20is%20also%20funded%20by%20OpenAI's%20startup%20fund%2C%20along%20with%20venture%20capital%20firms%208VC%20and%20Conviction%2C%20among%20others%2C%20the%20job%20listing%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJiang%20was%20OpenAI's%20third%20product%20manager%20and%20helped%20launch%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt-will-be-overhyped-overlooked-and-then-perhaps-essential-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emodels%20behind%20ChatGPT%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20the%20version%20that%20went%20viral%20in%20late%202022.%20She%20later%20worked%20on%20OpenAI's%20public%20policy%20team%20before%20leaving%20the%20company%20in%20December%202024%2C%20according%20to%20her%20LinkedIn%20profile.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWorktrace%20AI%20is%20the%20latest%20in%20a%20wave%20of%20highly%20valued%20AI%20startups%20founded%20by%20former%20OpenAI%20employees%2C%20many%20of%20which%20have%20secured%20major%20funding%20before%20launching%20a%20product%20or%20generating%20revenue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMurati's%20Thinking%20Machines%20Lab%20closed%20a%20mega%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmira-murati-new-ai-startup-thinking-machines-funding-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%242%20billion%20seed%20funding%20round%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20year%2C%20Business%20Insider%20previously%20reported%2C%20and%20it's%20now%20valued%20at%20%2412%20billion.%20Safe%20Superintelligence%2C%20founded%20by%20OpenAI's%20former%20chief%20scientist%20Ilya%20Sutskever%2C%20is%20valued%20at%20%2432%20billion%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2F792e09b2-f63b-41ac-8be8-e10e75ead2d1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFinancial%20Times%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20Periodic%20Labs%2C%20co-founded%20by%20William%20Fedus%2C%20one%20of%20the%20researchers%20who%20helped%20create%20ChatGPT%2C%20raised%20a%20%24300%20million%20round%20to%20build%20%26quot%3BAI%20scientists%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20announced.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20a%20tip%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20via