r%20packages%20coming%20to%20the%20US%20are%20marked%20for%20destruction%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226720%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Packages%20are%20being%20loaded%20onto%20UPS%20planes%20for%20shipment%20at%20the%20UPS%20West%20Coast%20Region%20Air%20Hub%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20Nov.%202%2C%202021%20in%20Ontario%2C%20CA.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68e92e1c1c1f80efbec55c88%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224480%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUPS%20says%20it%20has%20seen%20%26quot%3Ba%20significant%20increase%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20number%20of%20shipments%20that%20require%20formal%20customs%20clearance%20since%20new%20import%20rules%20have%20taken%20effect.%3Cp%3EIrfan%20Khan%20%2F%20Los%20Angeles%20Times%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ESome%20packages%20sent%20to%20the%20US%20from%20abroad%20are%20getting%20held%20up%20at%20UPS%20facilities%20for%20weeks.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENew%20rules%20on%20imports%20led%20several%20international%20carriers%20to%20suspend%20higher-value%20shipments%20to%20the%20US.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENow%2C%20unexpected%20information%20and%20fees%20are%20required%20to%20complete%20some%20shipments.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EUPS%20customers%20are%20finding%20their%20shipments%20stuck%20in%20package%20purgatory.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20customers%20of%20the%20shipping%20service%20say%20that%20packages%20sent%20to%20the%20US%20from%20abroad%20are%20getting%20held%20up%20at%20the%20carrier's%20facilities%20for%20weeks%20and%2C%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20are%20being%20subjected%20to%20higher-than-expected%20tariffs%20and%20customs%20brokerage%20fees%2C%20according%20to%20tracking%20information.%20Eight%20people%20whom%20Business%20Insider%20spoke%20to%20said%20that%20they%20received%20updates%20indicating%20they%20might%20never%20get%20their%20packages%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20package%20is%20undeliverable%20and%20is%20in%20the%20process%20of%20being%20disposed%20of%20according%20to%20the%20local%20guidelines%2C%26quot%3B%20reads%20one%20tracking%20update%20sent%20to%20several%20UPS%20customers%20Business%20Insider%20spoke%20with%20and%20posted%20widely%20on%20a%20subreddit%20for%20UPS%20users.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20many%20of%20these%20UPS%20customers%2C%20the%20delayed%20packages%20marked%20their%20first%20encounter%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftemu-order-shipping-cost-new-charges-trump-tariffs-how-explained-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Einternational%20shipping%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20era%20of%20tariffs%20imposed%20by%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20administration%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%20August%2C%20the%20Trump%20administration%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-end-of-de-minimis-creating-chaos-for-small-businesses-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eended%20the%20de%20minimis%20exemption%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20allowed%20foreign%20imports%20worth%20less%20than%20%24800%20to%20enter%20the%20US%20without%20being%20subject%20to%20tariffs.%20Personal%20gifts%20worth%20less%20than%20%24100%20are%20still%20allowed%20through%2C%20but%20the%20complexity%20of%20the%20new%20rules%20led%20several%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsome-european-postal-services-sellers-are-suspending-us-bound-shipments-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Einternational%20carriers%20to%20suspend%20higher-value%20shipments%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20UPS%20spokesperson%20said%20the%20company%20was%20seeing%20%26quot%3Ba%20significant%20increase%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20number%20of%20shipments%20that%20require%20formal%20customs%20clearance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20some%20UPS%20customers%2C%20the%20changes%20have%20meant%20that%20additional%20information%20or%20payments%20are%20required%20to%20complete%20certain%20shipments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKunal%20Sharma%2C%20an%20auto%20parts%20business%20owner%20in%20Canada%2C%20said%20he%20sent%20four%20car%20wheels%2C%20each%20in%20a%20separate%20box%2C%20to%20a%20customer%20in%20Texas%20in%20late%20August.%20He%20forgot%20to%20include%20the%20tariff%20codes%20for%20the%20wheels%20with%20the%20shipment%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUPS%20sent%20three%20of%20the%20four%20wheels%20back%20to%20him.%20The%20fourth%20still%20hasn't%20shown%20up%2C%20he%20said.%20Last%20week%2C%20its%20tracking%20page%20said%20the%20shipment%20was%20being%20disposed%20of%2C%20though%20it's%20since%20moved%20between%20UPS%20facilities%20in%20Ontario%2C%20Michigan%2C%20and%20Tennessee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAn%20entire%20set%20of%20wheels%20is%20worthless%20if%20one%20of%20them%20is%20missing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20Sharma%20emailed%20UPS%20CEO%20Carol%20Tom%C3%A9%20about%20the%20fourth%20wheel%2C%20a%20UPS%20customer%20relations%20employee%20apologized%20for%20the%20problem%2C%20in%20a%20message%20viewed%20by%20Business%20Insider.%20On%20Thursday%2C%20tracking%20indicated%20that%20the%20wheel%20was%20on%20its%20way%20to%20his%20customer%20in%20Texas.%20Sharma%20has%20started%20using%20FedEx%20to%20ship%20orders%20to%20his%20US%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBecause%20of%20changes%20to%20US%20import%20regulations%2C%20we%20are%20seeing%20many%20packages%20that%20are%20unable%20to%20clear%20customs%20due%20to%20missing%20or%20incomplete%20information%20about%20the%20shipment%20required%20for%20customs%20clearance%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20UPS%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20The%20spokesperson%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bmore%20than%2090%25%20of%20all%20imported%20packages%26quot%3B%20that%20move%20through%20UPS's%20network%20clear%20customs%20the%20first%20day%20that%20they%20arrive%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20packages%20that%20don't%20have%20complete%20customs%20information%20and%20when%20UPS%20cannot%20contact%20the%20shipper%2C%20the%20company%20either%20returns%20the%20package%20to%20the%20sender%20at%20their%20expense%20or%20disposes%20of%20it%20%26quot%3Bconsistent%20with%20US%20customs%20regulations.%26quot%3B%20The%20spokesperson%20did%20not%20provide%20details%20on%20how%20the%20disposal%20process%20works.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDavid%20Ordal%2C%20who%20lives%20in%20California's%20Bay%20Area%2C%20shared%20tracking%20information%20for%20his%20order%20of%20an%20annual%20supply%20of%20French%20sunscreen%2C%20which%20has%20been%20languishing%20for%20a%20month%20in%20Louisville%2C%20Kentucky.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20still%20not%20out%20of%20purgatory%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2248177656-6878-462f-8076-1b70bf8e0f23%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EUPS%20customers%20receiving%20shipments%20are%20also%20getting%20hit%20with%20unexpected%20costs%20or%20delays%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EKatie%20Golden%2C%20who%20resells%20vintage%20clothing%20on%20Depop%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20she%20ordered%20%24179%20worth%20of%20used%20apparel%20from%20the%20UK.%20The%20package%20left%20that%20country%20and%20made%20its%20way%20to%20UPS's%20facility%20in%20Louisville%2C%20Kentucky%2C%20according%20to%20a%20screenshot%20of%20UPS%20tracking%20information%20seen%20by%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUPS%20notified%20her%20that%20she%20had%20to%20pay%20%24769%20in%20import%20fees%2C%20including%20tariffs%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20UPS%20broker%20fee.%20At%20over%20four%20times%20the%20cost%20of%20her%20order%2C%20that's%20more%20than%20she%20was%20expecting%20to%20pay%20for%20used%20clothes%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGolden%20is%20currently%20trying%20to%20dispute%20that%20tariff%20amount%20with%20UPS.%20In%20the%20meantime%2C%20she%20said%20she's%20worried%20about%20her%20shipment%20being%20disposed%20of.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20going%20to%20keep%20bothering%20UPS%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20it's%20not%20just%20tariffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERecent%20changes%20to%20the%20Food%20and%20Drug%20Administration's%20review%20process%20for%20imports%20could%20also%20be%20causing%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20consultant%20in%20Los%20Angeles%20who%20is%20starting%20a%20coffee%20business%20told%20Business%20Insider%20she%20received%20two%20out%20of%2012%20boxes%20of%20inventory%20from%20Taiwan%20and%20was%20notified%20that%20the%20remaining%2010%20would%20be%20marked%20as%20abandoned%20and%20disposed%20of.%20She%20requested%20her%20name%20be%20withheld%20out%20of%20concern%20for%20her%20privacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22978%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20UPS%20tracking%20page.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68e94ce31c1f80efbec561e3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22821%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20tracking%20information%20page%20for%20one%20of%2012%20packages%20of%20coffee%20sent%20from%20Taiwan.%20The%20tracking%20number%20and%20US%20city%20have%20been%20redacted.%3Cp%3EUPS%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20recording%20of%20a%20call%20with%20UPS%20that%20the%20customer%20provided%20to%20Business%20Insider%2C%20an%20agent%20tells%20her%20that%20the%20FDA%20and%20Border%20Protection%20%26quot%3Bdecided%20to%20approve%20only%20a%20percentage%20of%20the%20shipment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20are%20getting%20very%20strict%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20UPS%20agent%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20they%20had%20received%20about%2010%20calls%20from%20other%20customers%20about%20similar%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHeather%20Elliott%2C%20who%20lives%20in%20Virginia%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20she%20ordered%20about%20%24750%20worth%20of%20French%20cosmetics%20in%20July%2C%20and%20was%20charged%20%24165%20when%20the%20shipment%20was%20processed%20at%20a%20UPS%20facility%20in%20Philadelphia.%20She%20paid%20that%20bill%20only%20to%20receive%20a%20second%20charge%20for%20roughly%20%24289.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20email%20exchange%20shared%20with%20Business%20Insider%2C%20UPS%20representatives%20itemized%20the%20charges%20as%20%26quot%3BPGA%20disclaimer%20(%2425)%2C%20disbursement%20fee%20(%2414)%2C%20entry%20line%20charge%20(%2445)%2C%20and%20FDA%20processing%20(%24111)%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20well%20as%20a%20duty%20of%20%2494.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EElliott's%20package%20was%20delivered%2C%20and%20UPS%20later%20refunded%20the%20initial%20%24165%20payment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20she%20has%20since%20ordered%20several%20shipments%20from%20a%20Korean%20retailer%20that%20have%20arrived%20via%20FedEx%20without%20any%20issues.%20A%20FedEx%20receipt%20Elliott%20shared%20with%20Business%20Insider%20shows%20a%20%24180%20order%20of%20personal%20care%20items%20that%20received%20a%20%2427%20duty%20charge%20and%20a%20%2427.50%20FDA%20clearance%20fee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227ff1cab8-6fb8-42a3-a815-ee7d6e7056b1%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESome%20UPS%20customers%20are%20turning%20to%20other%20delivery%20companies%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAlex%20Castellani%2C%20cofounder%20of%20Toronto-based%20coffee%20roaster%20Subtext%2C%20said%20that%20many%20of%20his%20shipments%20to%20the%20US%20since%20late%20August%20have%20sat%20for%20weeks%20at%20UPS%20facilities%20in%20Buffalo%2C%20New%20York%2C%20and%20Detroit%2C%20according%20to%20tracking%20information.%20That%2C%20plus%20higher-than-expected%20tariffs%20and%20broker%20fees%2C%20prompted%20him%20to%20switch%20to%20DHL%20for%20his%20US-bound%20shipments%20to%20caf%C3%A9s%20and%20individual%20consumers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20now%20paying%20more%20in%20brokerage%20and%20tariffs%20than%20the%20entire%20value%20of%20their%20package%2C%26quot%3B%20Castellani%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUPS%20has%20made%20changes%20this%20year%20in%20response%20to%20the%20Trump%20Administration's%20tariff%20policies.%20In%20April%2C%20the%20shipping%20service%20said%20that%20it%20would%20cut%2020%2C000%20jobs%20and%20shutter%20dozens%20of%20facilities%20in%20response%20to%20what%2