0spend%20time%20together%20as%20a%20family%2C%20others%20suggested%20it's%20going%20to%20rob%20their%20kids%20of%20building%20real-world%20skills%2C%20and%20a%20few%20were%20just%20there%20to%20find%20cofounders%20for%20their%20own%20startups.%20My%20mission%20was%20to%20simply%20see%20how%20parents%20are%20using%20the%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20unpacking%20the%20thrills%20and%20fears%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshielding-my-kids-from-ai-would-be-a-mistake-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20parenting%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20here's%20where%20parents%20seem%20to%20stand%20on%20raising%20the%20first%20generation%20of%20AI-native%20kids.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222e4a0e4e-f22e-4e07-b546-0cbdb30be540%5C%22%3EParents%20who%20work%20in%20tech%20are%20finding%20new%20ways%20to%20connect%20with%20their%20younger%20kids%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20the%20parents%20I%20spoke%20to%20or%20heard%20from%20at%20the%20event%20worked%20in%20the%20tech%20industry.%20Tarun%20Sachdeva%2C%20startup%20founder%20and%20dad%20of%207-year-old%20twin%20girls%2C%20was%20one%20of%20the%20speakers%20at%20the%20event%20and%20shared%20how%20AI%20allows%20him%20and%20his%20kids%20to%20become%20%26quot%3Bcreative%20partners.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20it%20has%20helped%20him%20connect%20with%20his%20kids%20in%20a%20way%20he%20never%20thought%20was%20possible.%20He%20now%20spends%20his%20weekends%20vibe%20coding%20with%20his%20girls%20on%20Cursor.%20They've%20created%20a%20puppy%20run%20game%2C%20KPop%20Demon%20Hunters-themed%20puzzles%2C%20and%20math%20worksheet%20games%2C%20all%20utilizing%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2263598993-f472-42ab-a061-00e3b182c9d9%5C%22%3EAI%20can%20lead%20to%20a%20more%20acceptable%20use%20of%20screen%20time%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fhow-much-screen-time-is-too-much%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EScreen%20time%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20a%20significant%20concern%20for%20parents%20during%20the%20Q%26amp%3BA%20portion%2C%20but%20when%20I%20spoke%20with%20Sachdeva%20after%20the%20event%2C%20I%20asked%20him%20if%20he%20ever%20has%20concerns%20about%20his%20kids'%20screen%20time%2C%20particularly%20when%20using%20AI.%20His%20answer%20surprised%20me%3B%20he%20has%20none.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESachdeva%20believes%20that%20AI%20has%20taken%20some%20of%20the%20negative%20aspects%20of%20screen%20time%20away%20from%20kids.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAI%20allows%20us%20to%20turn%20most%20of%20our%20interactions%20with%20the%20screen%20into%20creative%20interactions%20rather%20than%20purely%20consumption%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20actually%20think%20that%20screen%20time%20is%20something%20that%20is%20really%20misrepresented.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJohn%20Tidd%2C%20a%20dad%20of%20three%20young%20kids%2C%20said%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freddit-cofounder-alexis-ohanian-how-to-use-ai-kids-drawing-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ekids'%20favorite%20AI%20tool%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20the%20recently%20launched%20Gemini%20storybook%20feature%2C%20which%20allows%20them%20to%20create%20personalized%2C%20illustrated%20storybooks%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20using%20AI%20to%20create%20custom%20storybooks%20with%20his%204%20and%206-year-old%20boys%20allows%20them%20to%20tap%20into%20their%20curiosity%20and%20creativity%20together.%20Instead%20of%20separating%20them%2C%20%26quot%3Bcomputer%20lady%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20his%20boys%20call%20AI%2C%20%26quot%3Bjust%20adds%20a%20voice%20to%20the%20conversation%20instead%20of%20replacing%20one.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223103b3e7-3ccc-401c-ad93-173ad62bdd15%5C%22%3EParents%20still%20wonder%20when%20is%20the%20right%20time%20to%20allow%20kids%20to%20use%20AI%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%2045-minute%20breakout%20sessions%2C%20we%20were%20divided%20into%20three%20groups%20of%20around%20eight