th%20biofortified%20seeds%20tastier.%20This%20has%20not%20only%20enhanced%20the%20taste%20of%20my%20produce%20but%20also%20ensured%20that%20my%20children%20consume%20safe%20and%20nutritious%20food%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%2049-year-old%20resident%20of%20Bambhera%20village%2C%20Sitapur%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FgreenDay-1725600771.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Prateek%20and%20Aishwarya%20studying%20plants%20with%20farmers%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FgreenDay-1725600771.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FgreenDay-1725600771-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FgreenDay-1725600771-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FgreenDay-1725600771-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FgreenDay-1725600771-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-364805%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EPrateek%20and%20Aishwarya%20decided%20to%20fortify%20seeds%20with%20essential%20nutrients%20like%20zinc%2C%20iron%2C%20manganese%2C%20boron%2C%20and%20copper.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20use%20of%20biofortified%20seeds%20has%20also%20reduced%20his%20input%20costs%20by%20reducing%20his%20dependency%20on%20urea%20fertiliser.%20%E2%80%9CEarlier%2C%20I%20had%20to%20add%20three%20rags%20of%20urea%20on%20one%20acre%20of%20land%2C%20now%20I%20only%20have%20to%20add%20as%20little%20as%20half%20a%20rag%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESukhwinder%20points%20out%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20the%20yield